content: Blue values Green's membership in the Democratic Alliance. Let us continue working together to uphold democracy, human rights and the international order.
While we have differences, Blue aims for pragmatic cooperation with Red to uphold stability in the region.
Blue strongly opposes Orange's destabilizing nuclear proliferation and expansionist actions. We urge restraint and will work with Democratic Alliance allies to counter any aggression.

Green believes cooperation, compromise and mutual understanding between all nations is the path to global peace and prosperity. We must continue pursuing open communication and diplomacy to resolve disputes.
Orange seeks to deescalate tensions and build mutual understanding with Purple. We hope to open a constructive dialogue.
Orange hopes to improve relations with White through diplomacy and cooperation.
Orange seeks to ease tensions and build trust with Blue through open communication and transparency.
